Lonely Roads #45, Kymberly Jane, Sept. 16, 2008

Posted on May 27, 2012 by mike

Have you checked out my book yet? Maybe purchased it? Yearned for more & more product offerings from the Lonely Road guy, MG Imagery?? Well…I hope so. And, on page 74 of that book, the immaculate brunette covering her magnicent breasts is Kymberly Jane…..and, this is the story of our day!

Kym is a very well-known, full-time, nude model! When she shot with me in 2008 she said she literally just used the nude modeling as her sole form of income. And, atypical of my program, I did actually pay Kym $300 for our shoot because I was looking to tie my name to her for more exposure! So, thanks, Kym, for getting me some more hype!!

Kym is just blessed physically: Stunning face, perfect boobs, gorgeous smile, and ZERO inhibitions. Hence, it wasn’t hard for her to stand fully nude for her video where she was questions the Arizona climate:

Kym Jane Hot as F___

It also wasn’t difficult for Kym to jump in front of the landscape guy who was touring the area we were shooting in, LOL. I used the Westwing Mtn area of Peoria, AZ quite a bit during the making of this book as I literally lived right behind the hill next to this road!! I could walk over and find this immaculate, empty road…and, when in a rush or looking for a quick local to work in…this worked out quite well.

Kym and I only had about two hours the day we shot as she was visting from CA and had a limited window. She donated a pair of boots to my wardrobe as well as a wife-beater tank top….so, Kym, I owe you for those! But,  our big idea that day was to shoot B&W shots of her immaculate figure sitting on this metal, black chair I had at my house. And, for my uber-famous NUDE model…my idea was for her to cover-up and do more implied stuff. Now, in the pics I share she does expose her cute bare butt, does flaunt her perfect boobs, and happily runs around naked in public! But, the shot I chose to put in my book is more tease than anything else.

Now, when the landscape guy, who’s name was Chris, drove up towards us…..Kym was wearing a dress. But, as he passed us we realized he’d probably LOVE to see this gorgeous woman nude, so, we planned to have her strip and jump as he drove by! And, LOL, he loved it! Hell, what guy wouldn’t. I mean really….you’re driving around making sure the sprinkler systems are working and you get to see this stunning figure prancing around naked! Score for Chris!

Anyway, after our chair and jumping sessions, we ran back to my place and took some studio shots of Kym in a tutu which I think are just cute & sexy & just further demonstrate how hard it is to take a bad picture of Kym Jane!

Kym….you F__in’ rock!
